## Projects: Complete Extend S4Hana Cloud by using CAP <use cloud foundry enviroments>

---

Written by: Tungnx 


## Tài liệu

1. Consuming Services: https://cap.cloud.sap/docs/guides/using-services#execute-queries
2. SAP Cloud SDK For Javascript: https://sap.github.io/cloud-sdk/docs/js/overview
3. SAP Cloud SDK for excute odata services: https://sap.github.io/cloud-sdk/docs/js/tutorials/getting-started/execute-an-odata-request
4. Sample using Destination for call Api/Odata of SAP S4HANA Cloud: https://api.sap.com/api/API_SALES_ORDER_SRV/cloud-sdk/JavaScript
5. Using Authentication type for call Odata: https://sap.github.io/cloud-sdk/docs/js/features/connectivity/destinations

## Các services sử dụng trên BTP 
1. SAP S/4HANA Cloud Extensibility <Api-Access> - Check trong file manifest.yml <Extend-s4 và S4-test>
2. Authorization and Trust Management Service   - Check trong file manifest.yml <my-xsuaa>
3. Destination Service                          - Check trong file manifest.yml <my-destination> 
4. Cloud Foundry Runtimes 

## Sử dụng SAP Cloud Sdk nest Js 
- Sap Cloud Sdk là bộ dev kit dùng để làm Back-End và cung cấp ra các services 
- Muốn xây dựng front trên Project này, có thể sử dụng handlebar và render các file html làm UI  


